[Happy to pay a finders fee as well.   In cash or undercopies :) ]

Hey all - looking to find the following to fill holes in my set.  If you have any of the below in PSA 6-7 or know of anyone who does, please let me know.

Hoping some of these will surface as undercopies for those that picked up some of the recently auctioned #1 set (which was just unbelivable, by the way... :drooling:

The ones that have asterisks (**) i would take in PSA 5-5.5 as well, if that were all that was available.   And for the Plank, Magie, Demmit/STL and Ohara/STL, i'd go PSA 4-4.5



Thanks for any assistance!  
Joey
